Description: Many analysis workflows include approximation of a nearest
    neighbors graph followed by clustering of the graph structure. The
    concordex coefficient estimates the concordance between the graph and
    clustering results. The package 'concordexR' is an R implementation of the
    original concordex Python-based command line tool.
